{"tid":134174,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 香港踢波撚既辛酸","createTime":"2017-02-25T09:08:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T09:23:55.000Z","uid":9136,"like":5,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f2fd1df5ac215f73933476e247b3638872831ac","tid":134174,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:08:01.000Z","msg":"場已經夠少，仲要有時比d book場既自私廢物係假日霸住個場，有d場就永遠比d咁既細路每個星期六日都book<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/25/165155_838799ceedc93fe990be9a13e31c035c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F25%2F165155_838799ceedc93fe990be9a13e31c035c.jpg&h=15200302&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7a0HC3x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7a0HC3x.jpg&h=2de65d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上就係每個星期下晝其中一個場既情況，咁撚少人不如番屋企練啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> book撚哂成個場 仲要個個星期係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n附近有個細場 但有時比人搞埋d濕鳩嘉年華 屌你老母 而依個場就個個星期都比班1米都唔夠既細路練波 真係浪費資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 班細路行步路都行唔穩就學踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難為成班踢波撚想放假鬥下波都唔撚得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ac4ffd52a1f8b364c4e68c75d99be58ac33905","tid":134174,"uid":34772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:08:34.000Z","msg":"蓋清炒場狗黎"},{"pid":"244abc93eecab2f2e35699096ee38ff5b55a459c","tid":134174,"uid":22331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:08:39.000Z","msg":"d場俾蓋清hold起晒"},{"pid":"720e3a09848ce0930fa215f39ea7494b661ef078","tid":134174,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:24:15.000Z","msg":"其實覺得每個區都要有一個足球場唔book得<br />\n點解籃球場可以有街場而足球唔得"},{"pid":"5f14a48fe63a15df6b0b874aa57c4ca4ac2a8950","tid":134174,"uid":3229